Fit Simple Mediation Model for Data Generated from a Multivariate Normal Distribution with Data Missing at Random - Structural Equation Modeling

Source: R/mvn_mar_unstd_fit.sem.R
mvn_mar_fit.sem.Rd

Fit Simple Mediation Model for Data Generated from a Multivariate Normal Distribution with Data Missing at Random - Structural Equation Modeling

mvn_mar_fit.sem(data, taskid)

Arguments

data

n by 3 matrix or data frame. data[, 1] correspond to values for x. data[, 2] correspond to values for m. data[, 3] correspond to values for y.
taskid

Numeric. Task ID.

taskid <- 1
data <- mvn_dat(taskid = taskid)

# mvn_mar_fit.sem -------------------------------------------------
mvn_mar_fit.sem(data = data, taskid = taskid)
